plot: Blink-182's Urethra Chronicles is a fun look at the band's hilarious antics since they formed in 1992. Each current band member (Mark, Tom, and Travis) each have a five-minute bio where they delve into the details of their private lives as well as their band lives. Five studio videos (two from &"Dude Ranch&" and three from &"Enema of the State&") plus two live songs are also provided.   Written by  Matthew Sawyer
title: Blink-182: The Urethra Chronicles
